{
  "texts": [
    "For this reason, the timing of the prompt can yield varying results.",
    "Additionally, this proprietary model is updated without consideration for the researcher's timeline.",
    "As such, the model may change without the researcher's knowledge.",
    "There is very little a researcher can do to control for this so the best practice is to keep testing a prompt in the interests of consistent and stable results across multiple time points.",
    "The time between prompts is not the only temporal sensitivity involved with the model."
  ]
}